<div class="post">
	<h1 class="text-center">Endorsements</h1>
	<div class="entry">
		
<div class="wp-block-columns is-layout-flex wp-container-2 wp-block-columns-is-layout-flex">
<div class="wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow">
<div class="wp-block-media-text is-stacked-on-mobile has-black-color has-cyan-bluish-gray-background-color has-text-color has-background" style="grid-template-columns:24% auto"><figure class="wp-block-media-text__media"><img decoding="async" fetchpriority="high" width="1000" height="1000" src="https://brycereeves.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Lt.-Gov.-Winsome-Sears.png" alt="" class="wp-image-348 size-full" srcset="http://brycereeves.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Lt.-Gov.-Winsome-Sears.png 1000w, http://brycereeves.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Lt.-Gov.-Winsome-Sears-300x300.png 300w, http://brycereeves.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Lt.-Gov.-Winsome-Sears-150x150.png 150w, http://brycereeves.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Lt.-Gov.-Winsome-Sears-768x768.png 768w" sizes="(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px" /></figure><div class="wp-block-media-text__content">
<p class="has-medium-font-size">&#8220;Bryce has served his constituents well, getting even the toughest of bills out of a Democrat-controlled senate, and I am proud to endorse him for re-election.&#8221;</p>



<p><strong><em>-Lt. Gov. Winsome Sears</em></strong></p>
</div></div>



<div class="wp-block-media-text has-media-on-the-right is-stacked-on-mobile has-white-color has-text-color has-background" style="background-color:#202944;grid-template-columns:auto 23%"><div class="wp-block-media-text__content">
<p class="has-medium-font-size">&#8220;Thank you to Senator Reeves for his extraordinary leadership … (He) has been a tireless partner in working with me to keep Virginians safe.&#8221;</p>



<p><strong><em>-A.G. Jason Miyares</em></strong></p>
</div><figure class="wp-block-media-text__media"><img decoding="async" width="1000" height="1000" src="http://brycereeves.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/A.G.-Jason-Miyares.png" alt="" class="wp-image-355 size-full" srcset="http://brycereeves.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/A.G.-Jason-Miyares.png 1000w, http://brycereeves.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/A.G.-Jason-Miyares-300x300.png 300w, http://brycereeves.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/A.G.-Jason-Miyares-150x150.png 150w, http://brycereeves.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/A.G.-Jason-Miyares-768x768.png 768w" sizes="(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px" /></figure></div>



<div class="wp-block-media-text is-stacked-on-mobile has-black-color has-cyan-bluish-gray-background-color has-text-color has-background" style="grid-template-columns:23% auto"><figure class="wp-block-media-text__media"><img decoding="async" width="1000" height="1000" src="https://brycereeves.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Rep.-Bob-Good-.png" alt="" class="wp-image-356 size-full" srcset="http://brycereeves.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Rep.-Bob-Good-.png 1000w, http://brycereeves.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Rep.-Bob-Good--300x300.png 300w, http://brycereeves.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Rep.-Bob-Good--150x150.png 150w, http://brycereeves.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Rep.-Bob-Good--768x768.png 768w" sizes="(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px" /></figure><div class="wp-block-media-text__content">
<p class="has-medium-font-size">&#8220;(Bryce Reeves) is the conservative fighter we need to help Republicans regain majority control, so they can cut taxes, reduce government, &amp; protect our constitutional freedoms.&#8221;</p>



<p><strong><em><strong><em>-Rep. Bob Good</em></strong></em></strong></p>
</div></div>



<div class="wp-block-media-text has-media-on-the-right is-stacked-on-mobile has-white-color has-text-color has-background" style="background-color:#202944;grid-template-columns:auto 23%"><div class="wp-block-media-text__content">
<p class="has-medium-font-size">&#8220;(Bryce) looks out for law enforcement, fights to protect our shared history, &amp; is responsible for parental rights being codified into Virginia law. I couldn’t be prouder to have him as my Senator in Richmond.”</p>



<p><strong><em><strong><em>-Delegate Nick Freitas</em></strong></em></strong></p>
</div><figure class="wp-block-media-text__media"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="1000" height="1000" src="https://brycereeves.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Delegate-Nick-Freitas.png" alt="" class="wp-image-357 size-full" srcset="http://brycereeves.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Delegate-Nick-Freitas.png 1000w, http://brycereeves.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Delegate-Nick-Freitas-300x300.png 300w, http://brycereeves.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Delegate-Nick-Freitas-150x150.png 150w, http://brycereeves.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Delegate-Nick-Freitas-768x768.png 768w" sizes="(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px" /></figure></div>



<div class="wp-block-media-text is-stacked-on-mobile has-black-color has-cyan-bluish-gray-background-color has-text-color has-background" style="grid-template-columns:23% auto"><figure class="wp-block-media-text__media"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="1000" height="1000" src="https://brycereeves.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Delegate-Mike-Webert.png" alt="" class="wp-image-367 size-full" srcset="http://brycereeves.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Delegate-Mike-Webert.png 1000w, http://brycereeves.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Delegate-Mike-Webert-300x300.png 300w, http://brycereeves.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Delegate-Mike-Webert-150x150.png 150w, http://brycereeves.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Delegate-Mike-Webert-768x768.png 768w" sizes="(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px" /></figure><div class="wp-block-media-text__content">
